    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has clearly been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a strong luster, though you will find some light road wear such as minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with the leather upholstery showing only minimal bolsters wear. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly with a consistent service history, though the tires will likely need replacement within the next 10,000 miles. It offers a reliable and comfortable driving experience for its next owner.",
      "price": 35500.0,
