    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You've seriously got to see this car to believe it! It is in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready shape. I've babied this ride from day one\u2014it's always been garaged and has been kept in truly flawless condition. The interior is literally spotless and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks like it just rolled off the lot, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level example featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit, delivering peak torque through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, feeding power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable Lock differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to prevent floor fatigue, and the rod bearing service has been performed to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. The suspension maintains its factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and original-spec dampers, ensuring the chassis's legendary balance. Every fluid line, gasket, and seal remains in peak operational status, reflecting a true collector-grade specimen with zero evidence of oxidation or thermal cycling stress.",
      "price": 47800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. Clean title. No accidents.",
      "price": 43500.0,
