      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. It has been strictly garage-kept and treated with a premium ceramic coating to maintain its pristine appearance. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-new state; the high-grade leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously maintained with a full service history available, showing oil changes and preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, with no leaks or signs of aging. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been loved and pampered by a single enthusiast owner. If you are looking for perfection, this is it.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
